symposium.model

Class ScheduleData

  • java.lang.Object
    • symposium.model.ScheduleData

  • public class ScheduleData
extends java.lang.Object
    ScheduleData class is the main link between the model and the algorithm. the class hold all the information about the schedule, such as panelistAssigned, assignedPanels, unschedulablePanels, etc. Hence it is called the schedule data. The class also hold helper methods used in the constraints. The class is a singleton for the purpose of being used by almost all initializations of objects
